Package: MVNBayesian
Type: Package
Title:
  Bayesian Analysis Framework for MVN (Mixture) Distribution
Version: 0.0.8-11
Author: ZHANG Chen
Maintainer: ZHANG Chen <447974102@qq.com>
Description: Tools of Bayesian analysis framework using the method
  suggested by Berger (1985) <doi:10.1007/978-1-4757-4286-2> for
  a) calculating BP of MVN and (mixture) distribution;
  b) generating random vectors of MVN (mixture) distribution;
  c) MCMC simulation for MVN (mixture) distribution.
Imports:
  mvtnorm, plyr, stats
Suggests:
  rgl, Rfast
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/CubicZebra/MVNBayesian
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
